[Active]: When skill is activated, allies on her tiles gain 15% damage and 12% rate of fire for 5 seconds.

full_name: Višenamjenska Hrvatska Strojnica (Multifunctional Croatian Machine Gun)
name: VHS
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Obtains +1 stack of "Destruct" every second. For every stack of "Destruct" currently active, increases own final damage by 2.5% up to a max of 10 stacks.
[Active]: Consumes all stacks of "Destruct" and obtains damage/accuracy/rate of fire equivalent to the stat of the enemies with the highest respective stat. The stat gain is capped at 45% of self damage, 80% of self accuracy and 40% of self rate of fire. The effect lasts for 6 seconds and no stacks of "Destruct" can be gained throughout the skills duration.

name: PM1910
skill_desc:
[Passive]: During reloading state, allies on her tiles gain 20% Evasion, whereas allies not on her tiles gain 10% damage.
[Active]: Extends the current volley by +12 ammo. When using additional ammo, increases own accuracy by 80% and extends the next reload time by 4 seconds.

name: GM6_Lynx
skill_desc: Begin charging after skill cooldown ends, gaining 1 charge stack every second, up to a maximum of 5 stacks. When skill is used, shoot the current target thrice, dealing 1.7 ~ 3.2x damage per shot based on the current number of charge stacks, taking 0.5 seconds to aim before each shot. All stacks will be consumed on skill use.

name: TS12
skill_desc: Upon skill activation, the next 2 reloads have their reload time reduced to 0 seconds. Attacks after the first reload have 90% increased damage. Attacks after the second reload have 150% increased accuracy.

name: QSB-91
skill_desc:
[Passive]: If there are enemies near self, switch to knife mode. In this mode, every attack will deal 0.25x damage 4 times to the nearest target that cannot miss.
[Active]: Fire 4 consecutive shots with perfect accuracy at the current target, with each hit dealing 6x damage and ignores HP shields. Every shot requires 1 second of aiming.

name: LTLX_7000
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Reduces damage dealt to self from enemies directly ahead by 20%.
[Active]: Performs an attack that does not deal damage, forcibly knocking back moveable enemies within a 150-degree frontal cone of 6 unit radius ahead of self by 5 units, and remove the targets' HP shields and buff effects. Additionally, increases self armour by 20% for every target knocked-back (up to 5 stacks max) and reduce self damage by 0% for 8 seconds.

name: M6_ASW
skill_desc:
[Passive]: The first attack will consume all ammo and deal 4 hits. Whenever ammo is fully used up, switches to RF mode and change targeting mode to prioritise the furthest enemy from self. While RF mode is active, obtains the following stat changes: Reduced Evasion by 10%, increased rate of fire and damage by 100%, increased accuracy by 200%, increased armour piercing by +100 points.
[Active]: Reload and switches back to SG mode. Grants self a taunt effect until SG mode ends. Reload time is fixed at 2 seconds. When reloading ends, remove stat changes from RF mode and gains a +75 HP shield for 5 seconds. (Slug ammo only applies to normal attacks under SG mode)

name: V-PM5
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Whenever movement is made, grants self +9 movement speed which gradually decays within 9 seconds.
[Active]: Gains additional Evasion equal to 0.8x of armour value for 4 seconds.

name: HK512
skill_desc:
[Passive]: When reloading, reduce the current remaining reload time by 20% for self and other shotguns in the same column.
[Active]: Upon skill activation, increases own armour and Evasion by 20% for every shotgun in the echelon for 6 seconds.

name: SUB-2000
skill_desc: For every allied two/three-star rarity T-Doll on the field, increase said T-Dolls' damage, rate of fire, accuracy, Evasion and armour by 5% for 8 seconds. The buff increases based on the number of two/three-star T-Dolls present, up to a max of 25%.

name: AR-57
skill_desc: When skill is activated, grants effects based on the number of allies present on their buff tiles; If there is more than 2 allies present, increases damage by 15% for 2 seconds to self and allies on their tiles. If there is 2 or less allies present, increases Evasion by 40% for 2 seconds to self and allies on their tiles.

name: SVCh
skill_desc:
[Passive]: When changing attack targets, increases own damage by 10% for 5 seconds (stacks up to 4 layers).
[Active]: For 5 seconds, each attack from every dummy link carries an additional 150 points of fixed damage, ignoring enemy Evasion, armour and HP shields; When attacking enemies with multiple dummy links, the effect is doubled.

name: FX-05
skill_desc: Increases own damage by 40% for 15 seconds. While skill is active, for every layer of damage buffs obtained, increases own rate of fire by 5% until the skill ends (stacks up to 8 layers).

name: Kolibri
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Gain +1 Hummingbird every 2 seconds. If there are no allied units in the same column at the start of battle, gain +3 Hummingbirds instantly. Can hold up to 9 Hummingbirds. For every Hummingbird possessed, self attacks inflict an additional 1x damage.
[Active]: Consume all Hummingbirds and grant buffs to the entire team that last for 8 seconds. During the skill, no new Hummingbirds will be gained.
[1/2/3 Hummingbirds consumed]: Increase all allies' damage by 9%/16%/25%.
[4/5/6 Hummingbirds consumed]: On top of existing effects, increase all allies' rate of fire by 5%/12%/25%.
[7/8/9 Hummingbirds consumed]: On top of existing effects, increase all allies' critical hit rate by 20%/50%/100%.

name: Derringer
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Normal attacks fire 2 bullets, dealing 0.5x damage twice. If both bullets hit, deal additional damage equal to 5% of the enemy's lost HP (capped at 5x of self damage).
[Active]: Increase damage dealt by each bullet to 1x. Additional damage dealt is increased to 10% of the enemy's lost HP (capped at 5x of self damage). During the skill, attacks against enemies with less than 50% HP will never miss. The skill lasts for 5 seconds.

name: VP1915
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Attacks against enemies inflict an amplifying debuff that increases damage received by 3% for 8 seconds, stacking up to 5 layers. After 6 seconds, the debuff inflicted from attacks is doubled.
[Active]: Activate the skill to switch between the following modes;
[Strafing mode (default)]: Attack 2 enemies, dealing 1.2x damage each. Prioritize enemies that have not been attacked yet.
[Secure mode]: Deal 1.2x damage twice to the same enemy. The first hit will have perfect accuracy.

name: Savage_99
skill_desc:
[Passive]: At battle start, select a random target as prey. After participating in killing the prey, increase self damage by 45% and accuracy by +6 points. When the prey dies, select another random enemy as prey.
[Active]: Immediately target the enemy with the highest HP as prey and attack them until that unit dies. While skill is active, every attack increases self damage by 15%, stacking up to 5 layers and lasting until the current prey dies or the skill ends. The skill lasts for 5 seconds.

name: Fedorov
skill_desc:
[Passive]: When receiving DMG/ROF/EVA/ACC/CRIT buffs (including fairy talents), reduce current cooldown by 20%. Can only be activated once every skill cooldown.
[Active]: Permanently increases damage by 10%. The 3rd activation also increases rate of fire by 15%. The 5th activation also increases accuracy by 30%. Can be activated up to 6 times.

name: PPD-40
skill_desc:
[Passive]: For every ally in the same column, increase own damage and accuracy by 15%, stacking up to 2 layers.
[Active]: Increase all allies' damage by 22% for 8 seconds.

name: De_Lisle
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Whenever a dummy link deals a critical hit, add +1 layer of Marking on the target, stacking up to 15 layers. When an enemy reaches 15 layers of Marking, remove the enemy's HP shield and any Evasion or armour increasing effects, and reduce its Evasion and armour by 50% for 5 seconds. This effect can only be triggered once per target.
[Active]: Increase all allies' critical hit rate by 15%. Additionally, enemies with Marking receive +3% more damage taken per layer of Marking. Effects last for 5 seconds.

name: SIG_MCX
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Increase own damage dealt to targets under abnormal status by 20%. Normal attacks prioritize enemies under abnormal status. At the start of battle, gain 3 Taser charges. Gain +1 additional Taser charge every 10 seconds (can store up to 5).
[Active]: Consume 1 Taser charge and deal 3x damage to the nearest enemy with perfect accuracy. Additionally, apply the following effects to the target and enemies behind the target: stun the targets for 3 seconds and reduce their rate of fire and movement speed by 30% for 6 seconds (duration reduced by half against elite enemies).

name: RPK-203
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Allied SG on self tiles obtain position fortification effect; When receiving damage, place a teddy bear ahead of self that taunts enemies. This effect can be triggered once every 15 seconds for every unit, and the teddy bear inherits 5% Max HP, 50% Evasion, and 50% armour of that unit. Each teddy bear lasts for 5 seconds.
[Active]: Activate the skill to switch between the following modes;
[Continuous mode (default)]: Reduce own damage and accuracy by 10% and increase attack interval by 10%. No reloading is required while in this mode.
[Burst mode]: Increase own critical hit rate by 20% and critical hit damage by 40%, and attack the target with the highest HP. Every 4th hit will deal double damage.

name: TKB-408
skill_desc: During nighttime, Increases her damage and critical hit damage by 70% (28% during day) for 8 seconds. Additionally, if there are 3 or more gun types on field, increase critical hit rate by 30% (Does not apply during day battles).

name: SP9
skill_desc:
[Passive]: When there are 2 or more SMGs in the echelon, grants a +50 HP shield to the echelon at battle start and reduce initial skill cooldown by 15%.
[Active]: Reduce the damage stat of enemies within an area of 6 units ahead by 20, lasting for 8 seconds.

name: KH2002
skill_desc: After battle start, the Bulldog Pelé joins the fight, inheriting the following stats from KH2002; 600% damage, 80% rate of fire, 200% accuracy. This unit cannot be targeted, cannot crit and is unaffected by aura effects. When KH2002 retreats, Pelé also retreats. KH2002's final damage is reduced by 0% until the end of the battle.

name: APC556
skill_desc: When there are 3 or more ARs in the echelon, increase self damage by 40%. When receiving damage buffs, increase the echelon leader's damage by 50% of the current multiplicative damage buffs on self for 4 seconds. This effect cannot trigger other skill effects.

name: FARA 83
skill_desc:
[Passive]: When there are 3 or more ARs in the echelon, increase critical hit rate of allies within 1 tile of self by 25%.
[Active]: Record the stats of the ally with the current highest DPS, and return 110% of the recorded stats to that ally after 6 seconds. This effect lasts for 6 seconds. Within the effect period, the target's stats will be constantly overwritten by the recorded stats. This effect cannot trigger other skill effects.

name: MG338
skill_desc: Prioritize the enemy with the highest base damage. Can continue firing after running out of ammo, and only reloads when self DPS is the highest among all allies. Every attack increases self critical hit rate by 3% for 4 seconds, stacking up to 12 layers.

name: Noel
skill_desc: Dash towards the enemy and inflict 1.2x Noel's damage for 8 hits within a small area.

name: Elphelt
skill_desc: Inflicts 8x damage and locks on to the target before launching a missile that deals 12x damage to enemies within 1.5 unit radius.

name: Kiana
skill_desc: Generates a bolt of lightning that deals critical damage to enemies within a radius of 1.5 units. Enemies hit will be stunned for 3 seconds and will take 40% increased damage. (Does not affect boss units)

name: Raiden_Mei
skill_desc: Aims for 1.5 seconds and shoots the furthest target, dealing 5x damage and stunning them for 3 seconds. (Stun effect does not work on boss units)

name: Bronya
skill_desc: Throws out a grenade that produces a black hole after an explosion. The black hole lasts for 5 seconds and attracts enemies within a radius of 2.5 units. Enemies within 1.5 units from the center of the black hole will suffer 20% damage every second. This skill can only be used once per turn.

name: Theresa
skill_desc: Increases damage done to enemies by 100% within a radius of 5 units around self for 5 seconds, every attack has 30% chance to immobilise target for 2 seconds. (Does not effect boss units)

name: Murata_Himeko
skill_desc: For 5 seconds, charm (decrease damage by 30%) and fear (decrease movement speed by 30%) the nearest 3 enemies. At the same time, increases damage against feared enemies by 60%.

name: Seele
skill_desc: The last shot in her clip will deal 300% increased damage and cause her to reload instantly.

name: Clear
skill_desc: Stops attacking to put on 5 performances. Each performance increases a random allies' damage and accuracy by 30%(40% if "Glory Light" is equipped). Max 1 stack. Stacks last 3 seconds.

name: Fail
skill_desc: Stops attacking to put on 5 performances. Each performance decreases 3 random enemies' rate of fire and accuracy by 12%(15% if "Black Cat" is equipped). Max 2 stacks. Each stack lasts 3 seconds.

name: Jill
skill_desc:
[Passive]: For every point in Jill's base damage stat, Jill will receive 1% reduction to her skill's base cooldown up to a max of 30% base cooldown reduction (Unaffected by any DMG modifiers).
[Active]: After mixing in her cocktail shaker for 3 seconds, Jill will serve one of the following possible drinks to her echelon based on her current equipment loadout;
[Big Beer: Increases damage and accuracy by 25% and armor by 20% to all SG's for 8 seconds.],
[Brandtini: Increases damage and accuracy by 25% to all MG's for 8 seconds.],
[Piano Woman: Increases Evasion by 60% to all frontline allies. The remaining units will receive 20% increased damage instead, both buffs last for 8 seconds.],
[Moonblast: Increases rate of fire by 22% to all allies for 8 seconds.],
[Bleeding Jane: Increases critical hit rate by 25% to all AR's and RF's. If ally is over 100% crit rate, then 60% of excess crit rate will be converted to critical damage instead, buffs last for 8 seconds.],
[Fringe Weaver: Increases damage by 35% to all allies for 5 seconds, After initial buff expires, echelon receives a -15% damage and accuracy penalty for 3 seconds.],
[Sugar Rush: Increases damage by 18% to all allies for 8 seconds.]

name: Sei
skill_desc:
[Favorite Drink - Moonblast]: Shield's HP scaling is doubled.
[Active]: Grants a shield with 32 HP to all allied SG's, SMG's and HG's. The lower the HP of the ally, the higher the HP of the shield, ranging from 0.8x to 1.8x of the base value. Lasts for 5 seconds.
[Passive]: When Stella is present, Sei's attacks will be counted towards Stella's passive.

name: Dorothy
skill_desc:
[Favorite Drink - Piano Women]: Reduce the negative effects of her skill by 50%.
[Passive]: Dorothy will use Nano-camouflage by default if she is in the middle row, otherwise she will use MIRD113.
[Active]: Toggles between one of two skill effects;
[MIRD113: Increases damage by 100% but reduces the accuracy of allies in the same column by 40% and increases their Evasion by 80%.],
[Nano-camouflage: Increases Evasion by 100% but reduces the Evasion of allies in the same column by 40% and increases their accuracy by 80%.]

name: Stella
skill_desc:
[Favorite Drink - Bleeding Jane]: Puppets only require 10 attacks to activate her passive.
[Active]: Increases damage by 50% for 5 seconds.
[Passive 1]: When her puppets attack over 16 times, their next round of attacks does +50% critical damage.
[Passive 2]: When Sei is present, provide 10% reduction to her skill's base cooldown (Does not affect her initial cooldown).

name: Alma
skill_desc:
[Favorite Drink - Brantini]: Increase the duration of the drones by 1 second.
[Active]: Summons 2 additional drones to attack alongside her. The additional drones will deal 40% damage each and lasts for 4 seconds.

name: Dana
skill_desc:
[Favorite Drink - Big Beer] - Gains a 0.5 HP shield for every 1 point of armor Dana has.
[Passive]: Fires an exploding rocket fist. Can only attack 1 enemy, dealing 1.8x damage and has 10% chance of knockback (Does not stack with Slugs).
[Active]: Jumps up and smashes the ground, causing a large explosion dealing 0.6x damage and knockback to enemies within a radius of 2 units. Increases the damage of the skill by 1% for every 1 point of armor Dana has.

name: Henrietta
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Grants self a +10 HP shield at the start of battle, lasting for 8 seconds. If currently shielded, obtains +1 "Damage Mark" stack every 2 seconds up to a max of 3 stacks. For each "Damage mark" stack, increases self damage by 30% for 5 seconds. If not shielded, obtains +1 "Evasion Mark" stack every 2 seconds up to a max of 3 stacks. For each "Evasion Mark" stack, increases self Evasion by 20% for 5 seconds.
[Active]: Grants self a +10 HP shield for 8 seconds. For every stack of "Damage Mark", increases self rate of fire by 20%; For every stack of "Evasion Mark", grants self an additional +15 HP shield. Effects last for 5 seconds.

name: Rico
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Obtains +1 Tarot Card every 3 attacks up to a max of 3 Tarot Cards. Each Tarot Card held increases own damage by 15% for 5 seconds.
[Active]: Consumes all held Tarot Cards and deals 3x damage to the furthest target. This shot has perfect accuracy and can do critical damage. Additionally, deal an additional hit to enemies within a radius of 1 unit around the target. The damage of the additional hit is equal to 0.5x the number of Tarot Cards consumed up to a max of 1.5x damage.

name: Triela
skill_desc:
[Passive]: When there is an enemy unit within 2 units distance of herself, switches to using a bayonet to deal 2x damage to the nearest target. In this state, ammo is not consumed and rate of fire increases by 50% (does not work with Slug ammo). If there are no enemy units within 2 units distance of herself, increases max hit targets by +1.
[Active]: Increases damage by 80% and movement speed by +6 points for 8 seconds.

name: Claes
skill_desc:
[Passive]: While in Charging Mode, this unit cannot perform normal attacks. For every 2 seconds after a battle has begun, obtains +1 Charge up to a max of 5 Charges. For each held Charge, increases self damage by 25%.
[Active]: Enters attack mode. After ending attack mode and reloading, removes all damage increase from Charging mode and re-enters Charging Mode.
[EQ Passive 1]: When equipped with "Optical Glasses", Charging mode grants +8 HP shields to frontal allied units for 5 seconds, up to 3 layers maximum.
[EQ Passive 2]: When equipped with "Celestial Meteor", Charging mode increases all allies' damage by 5% for 5 seconds, up to 3 layers maximum.
[EQ Passive 3]: When equipped with "Wristwatch", Charging mode grants self +1 additional ammo into current clip.

name: Angelica
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Increases self damage by 12% at battle start. This buff gradually decays by 4% every 2 seconds, and is completely removed after 6 seconds. The buff will refresh itself every 10 seconds.
[Active]: Reduces own accuracy by -0% and increases rate of fire to a fixed 150 for 5 seconds.

name: Agent_Vector
skill_desc: Deploys a mobile cover ahead of self lasting for 8 seconds. The mobile cover will inherit 15% of the user's Max HP and gains a taunt effect on deployment.

name: Agent_416
skill_desc: Every 8 seconds, automatically place a sticky grenade on the enemy with the highest HP, up to a maximum of 3 grenades per enemy unit. When skill is activated, detonate all sticky grenades on the field, each dealing 5x damage that cannot miss within an area of 1.5 units.

name: Jashin-chan
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Jashin uses kicks as normal attacks, dealing dummy-linked damage in an area of 1 unit to the closest enemy. Kicks are affected by evasion and armour. Jashin gains HP shield equal to 10% of lost HP every 10 seconds.
[Active]: Jashin Flying Kick! Jashin deals a powerful kick to the enemy with the highest HP, gaining 1.5 seconds of invincibility during the skill. The kick deals 3.5x damage to enemies within an area of 1.5 units, and at least 1.5x damage to enemies within an area of 4 units. The more enemies there are in the center, the higher the damage dealt, up to 4.5x damage.

name: Pekora
skill_desc:
[Passive]: Pekora does not attack in default state. After receiving 5 layers of buffs, Pekora regains her angel's halo and can attack. Deals 1x damage that ignores armour and HP shields to the enemy with the lowest HP percentage, plus additional damage equal to 10% of the target's lost HP (cannot exceed 100% of the users damage), with a 15% chance of removing all of the target's buffs.
[Active]: Grants HP shield equal to 5% of self Max HP to all allies for 5 seconds.

name: Medusa
skill_desc: Randomly attack enemies and apply a mark to them. The mark reduces evasion and accuracy by 10%, lasts for 8 seconds and stacks up to 5 layers. Activate skill to petrify (stun) marked enemies, amplifying their damage taken by 10%. Each layer of mark increases petrification duration by 1 second. Every unit can only be petrified once.

name: Yurine
skill_desc:
[Active]: Cast magic on the enemy with the highest HP, dealing 2.5x damage to enemies within an area of 2.5 units and imprisoning them for 5 seconds.
[Passive]: After reloading, randomly gain 1 torture device to strengthen self.
[Trident]: Immediately grant +2 ammo to all allies and increase damage by 10% for 8 seconds.
[Iron Maiden]: Attacks reduce the target's rate of fire and movement speed by 10% for 4 seconds. After stacking to 5 layers, stuns for 3 seconds and deals 3x damage.
[Chainsaw]: Every attack deals an additional 0.25x damage that cannot miss and ignores armor and HP shield.

name: Minos
skill_desc: Rush to the front and stun enemies for 5 seconds, dealing 8x non dummy-linked damage plus additional damage equal to 20% of the enemy's Max HP. The additional damage cannot exceed 50x of the users damage. After reloading, Minos gains HP shield equal to 5% of Max HP. The HP shield cannot stack.

name: SAA Mod3
skill_desc: Increases all allies damage by 25% for 8 seconds.
skill2_desc: Increase all allies accuracy and rate of fire by 5% for every 4 seconds Colt Revolver remains on the field. Max 3 stacks.

name: M1911 Mod3
skill_desc: Throws a smoke grenade which decreases the enemy's rate of fire by 40% and movement speed by 50 within a radius of 2.5 units for 4 seconds.
skill2_desc: After tossing a smoke grenade, the next 7 attacks will strike in sequence from the furthest to the closest targets. Every hit will deal 200% damage.

name: Nagant Revolver Mod3
skill_desc: During nighttime, decreases all enemies damage by 40% (25% during daytime) for 8 seconds (5 seconds during daytime).
skill2_desc: Reloads after every 7 attacks. The first attack after reloading will increase all allies' damage and accuracy by 10% for 4 seconds.

name: Stechkin Mod3
skill_desc:
[Active]: Increases all allies' rate of fire by 25% for 8 seconds.
[EQ Passive]: When equipped with "Stechkin Exclusive Stock", increases allies' damage by 4% for the same skill duration.
skill2_desc: When "Assault Command" is active, increases own damage by 25% and critical rate by 100% for 8 seconds. For the duration of "Castanet Percussion", prioritise targeting enemies with the lowest health and reduces the Evasion of enemies with less than 30% health by 50% for 8 seconds.

name: Makarov Mod3
skill_desc: Decreases the enemy squads accuracy by 36% for 6 seconds. Additionally, grants all allies a shield equal to 60% of the HP of one Makarov Dummy-Link.
skill2_desc: When "Precision Suppression+" is active, increase accuracy and Evasion of the units with the worst accuracy and Evasion on her buff tiles respectively. The increase is equal to 50% of the difference between the target's and Makarov's own accuracy/Evasion.

name: C96 Mod3
skill_desc: Increases all allies accuracy by 120% for 15 seconds (night battles only).
skill2_desc: When Flare has been launched, grants allies +2 ammo to their current clip, additionally increases allies critical damage by 20% for 8 seconds.

name: MP5 Mod3
skill_desc: Grants self a barrier with a Defense value of 9999 (Max value of 9999), reducing incoming damage by a percentage (100% if at max Defense value) for 4 seconds.
skill2_desc: When Force Shield expires, increases Evasion by 20% for 8 seconds for every enemy group present, up to 3 layers.

name: Sten MkII Mod3
skill_desc: Throws a grenade that deals 6.5x damage to enemies within a 2.5 unit radius.
skill2_desc: 6 seconds after the battle begins, deploys a damage reducing shield in front of her that reduces all incoming damage by 35%, lasting for 5 seconds.

name: Beretta Model 38 Mod3
skill_desc: Throws a flashbang that stuns enemies within a 2.5 unit radius for 4 seconds.
skill2_desc: When flashbang has been tossed, throws an additional incendiary grenade that deals 2.8x damage to enemies within a radius of 2.5 units and ignites them, dealing 0.6x continuous damage to them every 0.33 seconds for 4 seconds.

name: Micro Uzi Mod3
skill_desc: Throws an incendiary grenade that deals 6.5x damage within a radius of 1.5 units and ignites them, dealing 1x continuous damage every 0.33 seconds for 5 seconds.
skill2_desc: Incendiary grenade deals an additional 0.8x damage every 1.5 seconds to burned enemies and will spread around the burned enemy, causing a new burning area with a radius of 1 unit. This lasts until the effect of the incendiary grenade ends. Burn damage will take effect against enemies in an extremely small area.

name: M14 Mod3
skill_desc: Increases damage by 65% for 5 seconds.
skill2_desc: When "Damage Focus" is active, increases critical damage by 10% for 6 seconds.

name: Mosin-Nagant Mod3
skill_desc: Begin charging after skill cooldown ends, gaining 1 charge stack every second, up to a maximum of 5 stacks. When skill is used, aim for 1 second, then deal 3 ~ 6.5x damage to the furthest enemy based on the current number of charge stacks. All stacks will be consumed on skill use.
skill2_desc: Every enemy unit that she kills, increases her damage by 20% for 3 seconds. (kills refresh this effect) Every enemy unit killed by her "Designated Shot" Skill, increases her rate of fire by 30% for 5 seconds.

name: SV-98 Mod3
skill_desc: Begin charging after skill cooldown ends, gaining 1 charge stack every second, up to a maximum of 5 stacks. When skill is used, aim for 1 second, then deal 2.8 ~ 6x damage to the nearest enemy based on the current number of charge stacks. All stacks will be consumed on skill use.
skill2_desc:
[Passive]: Enter camouflage mode after staying still for 3 seconds, and increase self accuracy and rate of fire by 8%.
[Active]: Using "Interdiction Shot" when in camouflage mode increases skill damage by 18% and removes camouflage.

name: Type 56 Mod3
skill_desc: Increases damage by 65% and movement speed by +5 points for 5 seconds.
skill2_desc: Prioritize attacking enemies with lower dummy links. For every missing dummy link below 5 dummy links, increase critical damage by 10%. Additionally, the first attack after moving will have doubled damage. This additional effect can be activated once every 3 seconds.

name: FN-49 Mod3
skill_desc: Increases damage by 65% for 5 seconds.
skill2_desc: Whenever "Damage Focus" is active, increases rate of fire by 15% for 5 seconds.

name: NTW-20 Mod3
skill_desc: Begin charging after skill cooldown ends, gaining 1 charge stack every second, up to a maximum of 7 stacks. When skill is used, aim for 1.5 seconds, prioritising the enemy with the highest health that can be killed in 1 shot (affected by link protection). If there are no enemies that can be instantly killed, prioritise the enemy with the highest health. After aiming, deal 5 ~ 10x damage that ignores HP shields based on the current number of charge stacks. All stacks will be consumed on skill use.
skill2_desc:
[Passive 1]: When "Hunter's Mania" kills an enemy, activate skill again and gain 3 Charge stacks. Can activate up to 3 times. The additional skill uses has no aiming time and does not gain bonus damage from Charge stacks, dealing 4x damage that can miss. It priorities enemies that can be instantly killed and which has the lowest health.
[Passive 2]: Increases damage of normal attacks and skills by 10% when attacking enemies with more than 50% HP.

name: M4A1 Mod3
skill_desc: Increases damage by 75% for 10 seconds.
skill2_desc: When "Damage Focus T" is active, apply Mark of Vengeance to the current target. In addition, once 3 or less allies are on the field, reduces self rate of fire by 70% and regular attacks do 600% damage, with an additional 100% splash damage to all targets within 2.5 units. This splash damage also applies Mark of Vengeance. ("Damage Focus T" is still in effect during this time).

name: M4 SOPMOD II Mod3
skill_desc: Launches a grenade that deals 15x damage to enemies within a radius of 1.5 unit.
skill2_desc: After her grenade detonates, it splits into 3 small grenades (Prioritises enemies marked by "Avengers Mark"). Each small grenade deals 190% damage to enemies within a radius of 1 unit, and inflicts 25% additional damage to enemies marked by "Mark of Vengeance".

name: ST AR-15 Mod3
skill_desc: Increases rate of fire by 50% for 15 seconds.
skill2_desc: When "Assault Focus T" is active, raises her secondary weapon and attack simultaneously, secondary weapon deals 10% of the primary damage, if the target is marked by "Mark of Vengeance" secondary weapon deals 20% instead.

name: AS Val Mod3
skill_desc: During nighttime, increases damage by 200% (70% during day) for 6 seconds.
skill2_desc: Upon receiving any type of damage buff (Including fairy skills and talents), grants self perfect accuracy for 3 seconds.

name: StG44 Mod3
skill_desc: Launches a grenade that deals 5/2/1x damage to enemies within a radius of 1/2.5/4 units.
skill2_desc: Base grenade damage increased by 20%, and will explode 3 times, dealing damage to enemies on the edges of the 1, 2.5 and 4 explosions radius. Enemies will receive multiple hits when standing in overlapping areas.

name: G3 Mod3
skill_desc: Launches a grenade that deals 12x damage to enemies within a radius of 1.5 units.
skill2_desc: Upon launching her grenade, have 1 of 2 effects happen depending on how much HP her targets has. If targets have over 50% HP, applies a stun effect that lasts 1.6 seconds. If targets has under 50% HP, her grenade will deal an extra 4x damage.

name: G36 Mod3
skill_desc: Increases damage by 75% for 10 seconds.
skill2_desc: When "Damage Focus T" activates, increase the Evasion of allies on her buff tiles by 25% for 5 seconds. For every ally present on her buff tiles during the passives activation, grants self 10% rate of fire for 5 seconds (Max 2 stacks).

name: HK416 Mod3
skill_desc: Launches a grenade that deals 16x damage to enemies within a radius of 1.5 units.
skill2_desc: If grenade kills the main target, cause a secondary explosion dealing 3.5x damage to enemies within a radius of 4 units. If grenade did not kill the main target, deal 0.6x damage every 0.33 seconds and increases damage dealt to the target by 20% for 3 seconds.

name: Galil Mod3
skill_desc: Increases accuracy by 550% for 15 seconds.
skill2_desc: When self accuracy is higher than enemy Evasion, 20% of the overflow accuracy will be added as critical rate to self, however the critical rate increase cannot bring it above 100%. All AR/SMG T-Dolls on Galil's tiles will gain 10% of Galil's accuracy. Thereafter, decrease Galil's accuracy by 20% for every AR/SMG on her tiles.

name: M1918 Mod3
skill_desc: Increases damage by 75% for 6 seconds.
skill2_desc: Self reload time is reduced to a fixed 5 seconds. After reloading, the first 3 bullets will have 40% increased damage (affects first volley).

name: LWMMG Mod3
skill_desc: Increases accuracy by 70% and causes all hits to be guaranteed critical hits for 6 seconds.
skill2_desc: Every attack she does has a 20% chance to grant a 5 HP shield to dolls on her tiles, lasting for 6 seconds. While "Hunting Impulse" is active, increases the chance of granting a shield to 100%.

name: Bren Mod3
skill_desc: Increases damage by 30% and grants +4 ammo to current salvo for 8 seconds.
skill2_desc: Increases accuracy by 15% and increases max ammo by +1 for every reload. Can be stacked up to 3 times.

name: MP-446 Mod3
skill_desc: Decreases the enemy squads rate of fire by 28% for 8 seconds.
skill2_desc: Upon activation of "Assault Suppression", increases the rate of fire of allies on her tile buffs by 20% for 4 seconds.

name: IDW Mod3
skill_desc: Increases Evasion by 130% for 5 seconds.
skill2_desc: Start a battle with 3 bars of battery, each bar increasing rate of fire by 10% and damage by 20%. Consumes 1 bar of battery every 2.6 seconds. When IDW uses Cover Focus, battery replenishes back to 3.

name: Type 64 Mod3
skill_desc:
[Active]: Throws a flashbang that stuns enemies within a 2.5 unit radius for 4 seconds.
[EQ Passive]: When equipped with "High Performance Camouflage Exoskeleton", enemies stunned by Type 64's stun grenade will lose all beneficial stat modifications and HP shield effects.
skill2_desc: Thrown flashbang will also incur a 40% accuracy penalty to struck units which lasts for 8 seconds. Units that are immune to stuns are also affected.

name: Hanyang Type 88 Mod3
skill_desc: During night, increases damage by 100% (35% during day) and movement speed by 500% for 6 seconds.
skill2_desc:
If there are enemies directly in front of her, switch to attacking with an energy blade sending out waves of energy dealing 1x damage to all enemy units in the same lane as her.
When Damage Focus N is active: Attacks gain a piercing effect, dealing 1x damage to all enemies it passes through. Additionally perform one of two actions based on the enemies status;
If they're armoured and has the highest HP, fire a missile dealing 1.5x damage to the target and dealing 0.5x damage to enemies within a radius of 2 units. Splash damage is affected by armour.
If they're unarmored, throw a cluster grenade which will deal 0.5x damage within a radius of 1 unit repeatedly up to 7 times. Repeated explosions on the same target will only deal 0.25x damage. Grenade damage can be evaded and is affected by armour.

name: M950A Mod3
skill_desc: Increases all allies' rate of fire by 28% for 8 seconds.
skill2_desc:
When entering combat on an allied node, create a deceleration zone in a radius of 4 units in front of the echelon's formation, reducing the movement speed and Evasion of enemies within by 30% for 6 seconds.
When entering combat on a non-allied node, increase all allies' rate of fire by 5% for 5 seconds. Additionally, increase SMG/RF/AR/MG/SG movement speed by 3/8/5/11/9 points for 60 seconds.

name: UMP9 Mod3
skill_desc: Throws a flashbang that stuns enemies within a 2.5 unit radius for 4.5 seconds.
skill2_desc:
If the main target of the flashbang was not stunned or is already dead, grants a 25 HP shield and 25% Evasion to self and allies on the same column for 5 seconds.
If the main target of the flashbang was stunned, increase the damage of self and allies on the same column by 50% for 5 seconds.

name: UMP45 Mod3
skill_desc: Throws a smoke grenade that decreases the enemy's rate of fire by 40% and movement speed by 55% within a radius of 2.5 units for 4 seconds.
skill2_desc: 2 seconds after smoke grenade takes effect, targets affected by the smoke grenade will be hacked every 2 seconds. Hacked targets will enter a short-circuited state, receiving 50 fixed damage every attack. Short-circuit state lasts for 5 seconds.

name: Welrod MkII Mod3
skill_desc:
[Active]: Decreases the enemy squad's accuracy by 45% and damage by 15% for 6 seconds.
[EQ Passive]: When equipped with "Special Ops Go Bag", increase self rate of fire by 30% and reduce damage taken by 30% from enemies attacked by self.
skill2_desc: Upon receiving damage, place a blast shield in front of self. Units behind the blast shield will become invulnerable until the blast shield is removed. The blast shield has 15 HP and only receives 1 damage each hit. It inherits 30% of Welrod's Evasion and is immune to damage lower than 30% of Welrod's single-dummy Max HP. The blast shield lasts for 4 seconds and has a cooldown of 8 seconds.

name: G11 Mod3
skill_desc: Each attack will inflict 3x hits on the target for 5 seconds.
skill2_desc: For every 3 hits on the same enemy, deal an extra hit that does damage equal to 2% of the enemy's max HP. The extra hit is affected by armour but ignores HP shields, and cannot exceed 300% of self damage.

full_name: Armalite SUPER Semi Automatic Sniper System
name: Super SASS Mod3
skill_desc: Begin charging after skill cooldown ends, gaining 1 charge stack every second, up to a maximum of 5 stacks. When skill is used, aim for 1 second, then deal 2.8 ~ 6x damage to an enemy with the highest HP based on the current number of charge stacks. All stacks will be consumed on skill use.
skill2_desc:
[Passive 1]: When "Aimed Snipe" fails to kills an enemy, repeatedly snipe the target based on the number of Charge stacks, until the target dies or the Charges run out. The additional snipes are strengthened auto-attacks, dealing 1x damage with perfect accuracy. This shot can do critical damage, but doesn't ignore armour.
[Passive 2]: Increases damage of normal attacks and skills by 10% when attacking enemies with less than 50% HP.

name: MG4 Mod3
skill_desc: Increases damage by 50% and grants +6 ammo to current salvo for 8 seconds.
skill2_desc:
Prioritize using the extra ammo from "Lock and Load", converting 25% of any excess armour-piercing stat into damage. While skill is active, shots using extra ammo will also increase damage by 5% for 18 seconds to a max of 8 stacks.
[EQ Passive]: When equipped with "Mk4 SLAP", shots will ricochet and deal 0.1x damage up to 3 times. Hit targets also have their damage reduced by -1 point for 6 seconds to a max of 8 stacks.

name: PP-19 Mod3
skill_desc: Throws a grenade that deals 7.5x damage to enemies within a radius of 2.5 units.
skill2_desc:
Skill 1 will mark enemies damaged by the grenade. If there are marked enemies still alive, PP-19's remaining dummy links will successively throw 1 additional grenade each at marked enemies, dealing 3x damage to enemies within a radius of 2.5 units.
[EQ Passive]: When equipped with "PT-3 Buttstock", every 6 seconds, check PP-19's HP. If PP-19's HP is the highest in the column, increase own damage by 10%, otherwise increase own Evasion by 10%. Each buff lasts for 15 seconds (stackable).

name: RO635 Mod3
skill_desc: Increases self Evasion by 70% while decreasing enemies damage by 25% and accuracy by 10% for 5 seconds.
skill2_desc: When receiving damage lower than the HP of a dummy link, there is 20% chance to check Evasion again. If the check succeeds, no damage is taken. For every layer of DMG/ACC/ROF/MS reduction effects or "Mark of Vengeance" on the attacker, the activation chance of the Evasion check increases by an additional 10%. When "Mental Deterrence" is active, self attacks will inflict "Mark of Vengeance" on the target.

name: M1897 Mod3
skill_desc: Performs an additional attack which deals 2.5x damage pushes back targets back by 3 units.
skill2_desc: Every time an allied unit on the field performs a reload, M1897 gains +1 flechette. M1897 will prioritize using any held flechettes, each dealing 1 attack with 20 hits of 1x damage. The multiple hits cannot knockback enemies and will be randomly distributed among enemies within attack range. Consecutive hits on the same enemy will have the damage reduced by 30% with each hit, to a minimum of 10% of the original multiplier.

name: M500 Mod3
skill_desc: Increases own armour rating by 70% for 6 seconds.
skill2_desc: When receiving DMG/ROF/EVA/ACC/CRIT/ARMOUR increasing effects from skills (including fairy talents), if there is another ally in the same column, grants a 25 HP shield to self and allies in the same column for 5 seconds. Stacks up to 3 times.

name: RMB-93 Mod3
skill_desc: Performs an additional attack which deals 2x damage and pushes back targets back by 3 units. Damaged targets will also be amplified, increasing the damage they take by 10% for 8 seconds.
skill2_desc: When an ally reloads, reduce incoming damage taken by -4 points to a max of 3 stacks for 8 seconds.

name: Type 97 Shotgun Mod3
skill_desc: Increases damage by 120% and accuracy by 20% and increases the amount of targets hit per attack to 5 (overwrites the effect of Slugs), last for 8 seconds.
skill2_desc: Reduces the movement speed of hit enemies by 50% for 1 second.

name: F1 Mod3
skill_desc: Throws a smoke grenade that decreases the enemy's rate of fire by 40%, movement speed by 50%, and accuracy by 30% within a radius of 2.5 units for 4 seconds.
skill2_desc: When echelon is on a non-allied node, permanently increase all allies' movement speed by +5 points and damage by 15%.

full_name: 80式通用机枪 (Type 80 General Purpose Machine Gun)
name: Type 80 Mod3
skill_desc:
[Passive]: When changing targets, the first shot on the new target deals an additional 50% damage.
[Active]: Increases damage by 75% for 6 seconds.
skill2_desc: Allied MG/SG on self tiles obtain position fortification effect: When within her tiles, increase movement speed by +10 points. When Type 80's "Damage Focus MG" skill is active, enhance the fortification effect on allied MG/SG: Increase damage by 20%; Gain +10 HP shield that lasts for 6 seconds after every reload.

name: XM3 Mod3
skill_desc: During nighttime, increases rate of fire by 110% (35% in during day) and prioritise attacking the enemy unit with the lowest HP for 5 seconds.
skill2_desc: When the "Assault Focus N" is in effect, her first attack on a target will have perfect accuracy and do critical damage. The critical damage of this attack is also increased by 20% (The critical damage buff only takes effect in nighttime).

name: GSh-18 Mod3
skill_desc: Pulls out a secondary handgun and dual wields for 8 seconds, dealing guaranteed critical damage per shot while skill remains active.
skill2_desc: Every attack has a chance to grant 1-HP shields to allies on her tiles, where the chance is equal to her critical rate. The shields last for 60 seconds and can be stacked infinitely. Additionally, increase self critical damage by 20% while "Chain Assault" is active.

name: KSVK Mod3
skill_desc: Begin charging after skill cooldown ends, gaining 1 charge stack every second, up to a maximum of 5 stacks. When skill is used, aim for 1 second, then deal 2.6 ~ 5x damage to the nearest target based on the current number of charge stacks. All stacks will be consumed on skill use; Additionally, deal 0.5x damage to enemies in a 2 unit radius behind the target and decrease their accuracy and rate of fire by 20% for 5 seconds.
skill2_desc: When any enemy unit is under a negative status effect, changes basic attacks to [Shock Grenade] mode. Prioritize attacking the nearest enemy under negative status and deals an additional 0.3x damage to enemies within a radius of 2 units behind the target.
